<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>139</hymn_number>
<title>yà bó lā hǎn de gù shì 迦南139</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yà bó lā hǎn qī shí wǔ suì lí kāi gù xiāng,
 bù zhī dào qù nà lǐ, lù zài hé fāng
 dàn shén yǐ xiàng tā fā chū yán yǔ,
 lì kè qǐ chéng yíng fēng yǔ, dǐng jiāo yáng,
 jīng guò le zhàng péng de shēng huó, yòu jīng guò jī huāng,
 dàn tā shǐ zhōng xìn shén shì tā yǒng yuǎn de bǎo zhàng,
 yé hé huá yīn qí xìn chēng tā wèi yì,
 bǎ tā dài jìn méng fú zhī de, měi míng chuán wàn bāng;
 yà bó lā hǎn wǒ men xìn xīn de hǎo bǎng yàng,
 hái yǒu tā de jiàn zhèng jì zài shèng jīng shàng,
 xìn xīn de wěi rén, duō guó zhī fù,
 tā xīn zhōng pàn wàng de shì lìng yī gè jiā xiāng.</lyrics>
</song>